---
title: Coconut-Crusted Chicken Fingers with Green Beans and Sweet Potato Fries
description: Crispy panko and flaky coconut give ordinary chicken fingers a major boost. For a smoky-sweet twist on oven baked fries, we're sprinkling these sweet potatoes with a touch of paprika.
